author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how across the board one company has just started to jack up prices for their gaming console. Typically these things go down in price overtime but I want to welcome you to the generation where video games just keep getting more expensive. Thanks for watching!

title: Playstation Is Being Greedy...
